    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2>《西格洛夫的低语》是一款心理恐怖游戏，这个世界充斥着光明与黑暗，盛放的生命和腐朽的现实在此交织，你也会逐渐了解光的真实力量。身为西树林精神病院的001号病人，你发现梦中的行动会影响现实。你必须利用这项能力，在凯德医生愈发危险的治疗手段彻底毁掉你之前逃出生天。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228840/extras/a51f53db22d7b61a313651f1fa4f0248.poster.avif?t=1764184548\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228840/extras/a51f53db22d7b61a313651f1fa4f0248.webm?t=1764184548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228840/extras/a51f53db22d7b61a313651f1fa4f0248.mp4?t=1764184548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你的记忆不再清晰，需要在梦境中游历并寻找物品与线索，帮助自己回忆过去。然而，探索西格洛夫镇时必须处处小心，梦境可能随时化为噩梦，你可能会被精神病院的怪物追逐，危险无处不在。一定要找到武器、补给以及其他幸存者来生存下去，进入绝境时，可以尝试改变光的方向，用智慧战胜敌人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228840/extras/53f0d4f11bc7ab93917bf8b00cf64a0f.poster.avif?t=1764184548\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228840/extras/53f0d4f11bc7ab93917bf8b00cf64a0f.webm?t=1764184548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228840/extras/53f0d4f11bc7ab93917bf8b00cf64a0f.mp4?t=1764184548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>这段旅程困难重重，每个梦境中都有独特的谜题与全新的敌人，是对你的作战能力与解谜能力的双重考验。<br><br>打磨好技巧，也要打磨好武器。学会运用多种策略来躲避或对抗敌人。每种武器都有独特的能力，能够用于进攻或防御两种玩法。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228840/extras/f9f48bc3a3ebd4cacc74ca2a4c062e49.poster.avif?t=1764184548\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228840/extras/f9f48bc3a3ebd4cacc74ca2a4c062e49.webm?t=1764184548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228840/extras/f9f48bc3a3ebd4cacc74ca2a4c062e49.mp4?t=1764184548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >剧情主线</h2><u>序章</u><br>故事发生在1960年代。你在一次严重事故后精神崩溃，被送入西格洛夫精神病院接受治疗。你被安置在重症病区，由首席医生凯德负责。不过，凯德医生似乎有些不对劲，你发现他开始对病人进行越来越极端的治疗，也意识到自己陷入了危险之中。<br><br><u>梦境世界</u><br>在一次失败的脑叶切除术后，你失语了，而噩梦也在此时开始。阴影中的怪物、被绑架的病人、幻境中的低语，都是不祥之兆。这些反复出现的梦境逐渐渗入白昼，梦与现实的界限也变得越来越模糊。你唯一的希望，是利用那只神秘的手电筒来改变你对世界的感知。但要小心……别让自己迷失在虚幻之中。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228840/extras/3892f7f6864cdcb4c28aa2afb6eb46f7.poster.avif?t=1764184548\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228840/extras/3892f7f6864cdcb4c28aa2afb6eb46f7.webm?t=1764184548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228840/extras/3892f7f6864cdcb4c28aa2afb6eb46f7.mp4?t=1764184548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
